member.name: IAppxManifestReader2.GetQualifiedResources
member.summary: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the qualified resources that are defined in the manifest.
member.param: The enumerator that iterates through the qualified resources.
member.returns: If the method succeeds, it returns S_OK.
